<span class="line"><span style="color:#E1E4E8;">-v </span><span style="color:#9ECBFF;">/path/to/your/data/dir:/usr/src/app/data</span><span style="color:#E1E4E8;"> </span><span style="color:#79B8FF;">\\ </span><span style="color:#9ECBFF;">#</span><span style="color:#E1E4E8;"> </span><span style="color:#9ECBFF;">请替换</span><span style="color:#E1E4E8;"> </span><span style="color:#9ECBFF;">/path/to/your/data/dir</span><span style="color:#E1E4E8;"> </span><span style="color:#9ECBFF;">为您想存储接口持久化数据的目录绝对位置</span></span>
